MAX PACK SIZE = 1300 (id, type and data included)

every number shall be transfered in little endiannes

packet:
	6 byte: id (server respond to query with same id)
	2 byte: type 
	... (data)

"->": what the client send
"<-": what the server send

get package id:
	-> 0x01
	-> package name (end of the packet)

	<- 0x02
	<- package id (8 bytes, == 0 if notfound)

get package info:
	-> 0x03
	-> package id (8 bytes)

	success:
		<- 0x04
		<- package size (8 bytes)
		<- package info (1000 character description)
	fail:
		package is being updated:
			<- 0xFF00
		invalid package id:
			<- 0xFF01

read package part:
	-> 0x07
	-> package id (8 bytes)
	-> offset (8 bytes)
	-> length (2 bytes)

	success:
		<- 0x08
		<- data (at most `length' bytes)
	
	fail:
		offset out of range:
			<- 0xFF03
		length too long:
			<- 0xFF04

get package dependencies:
	-> 0x09
	-> package id (8 bytes)

	success:
		<- 0x0A
		<- dependencies ids (8 bytes each)
	fail:
		package is being updated:
			<- 0xFF00
		invalid package id:
			<- 0xFF01
		

type 0xFFFF: unknown request
